// Camera shake effect configuration
// Uses a "trauma" model: each large merge adds trauma (0–1) that decays
// over time. Camera displacement = trauma² × max_offset.
//
// Hot-reload enabled: Edit this file while the game is running!
//
//   decay           - Trauma lost per second. Higher = shorter shake.
//                     Recommended range: 3.0 – 10.0
//   max_offset      - Maximum camera displacement in pixels at trauma = 1.0.
//                     Recommended range: 8.0 – 25.0
//   min_fruit_index - Minimum fruit index (0-based) that triggers a shake.
//                     0=Cherry … 5=Apple … 10=Watermelon
//                     Fruits below this index cause no shake.
//   intensity_step  - Trauma added per index step above min_fruit_index.
//                     e.g. at 0.15: Apple adds 0.15, Pear 0.30 … Watermelon 0.90

ShakeConfig(
    decay: 3.5,
    max_offset: 12.0,
    min_fruit_index: 4,
    intensity_step: 0.2,
)
